'''Fontaine''' is a [[Charleroi Metro]] station, located in [[Fontaine-l'ÃvÃªque]], in fare zone 7. It is an underground station featuring a central platform with street access at its western end.
The station has been refurbished in 2009-2010 and its current version was inaugurated on 16 June 2010.<ref>M.C., [http://www.lavenir.net/article/detail.aspx?articleid=38866753&postcode=6000 "Une station complÃ¨tement rÃ©novÃ©e"], ''L'Avenir'', Charleroi, 17 June 2010.</ref> The interior decoration, made of colored castle-like shapes on a white background, is a work of architect Ingrid Lange.
